1. *Imaćemo* sastanak u 10 sati. (We will have a meeting at 10 o'clock.)
2. Vidim da *imaćemo* lijepo vrijeme sutra. (I see that we will have nice weather tomorrow.)
3. *Imaćemo* tri gosta na večeri. (We will have three guests for dinner.)
4. Moramo se potruditi da *imaćemo* dovoljno vremena za sve. (We have to make an effort to have enough time for everything.)
5. Kad *imaćemo* taj seminar? (When will we have that seminar?)
6. *Imaćemo* problem ako ne riješimo ovu situaciju na vrijeme. (We will have a problem if we don't solve this situation in time.)
7. Znam da *imaćemo* puno posla ovaj tjedan. (I know that we will have a lot of work this week.)
8. *Imaćemo* priliku da upoznamo neke zanimljive ljude na konferenciji. (We will have the opportunity to meet some interesting people at the conference.)
9. Mogu li *imaćemo* malo više vremena da se odlučimo? (Can we have a little more time to decide?)
10. *Imaćemo* sve što nam treba za ovaj projekt. (We will have everything we need for this project.)